Baby Dreams Soothing Powder (100 g) Price: Rs.40

Taking care of infants can be a lot fun with the right products. Attending to a baby’s fragile skin can be a little apprehensive as they are prone to infections and irritations very quickly. The Morisons Baby Dreams Powder is a special formulation that has been made to heed to the various needs of a baby’s skin. This Baby Powder is made by inculcating the goodness of various ingredients such as Zinc Stearate
column13:
extra virgin oil and fragrance. Zinc Stearate a practically non-toxic compound has properties of a sunscreen that protect your little one\u2019s skin from the harmful effects of the sun.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis soothing and protective Talcum Powder from Morisons Baby Dreams Collection will leave your child\u2019s delicate skin refreshed and free of any unwanted moisture. The mild and comforting talc from Morisons can be used on your baby\u2019s skin after nappy changes
column14:
before sleeping and after bathing to keep the baby\u2019s skin fresh.
